msgctxt "124\t256\t132\t\t \t "
msgid ""
"Have you ever thought of leaving\r\r\n"
"this place, Kazuma Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277\t338\t61\t　\t　\t "
msgid "I'm not sure what you're getting at."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "483\t592\t109\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"It's been a week now since I met\r\r\n"
"your daughter in that Ryukyu bookstore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "617\t816\t199\tOK\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Since then, I've spent my time researching both\r\r\n"
"her and this orphanage. Quite thorougly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "846\t955\t109\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Of course, I'm aware of your history."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1051\t1111\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Haruka Sawamura."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1142\t1267\t125\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Her appearance and sense of style are unpolished,\r\r\n"
"yes, but she shows undeniable potential."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1275\t1335\t60\t分\t　\t "
msgid "She just needs her edges smoothed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1341\t1520\t179\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"With time, I'm confident I can make her\r\n"
"the most dazzling jewel anyone's ever seen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1668\t1814\t146\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Entrust her to me, and she'll be a star."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1870\t1930\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "On one condition, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1958\t2035\t77\t　\t　\t "
msgid "You want me out of the picture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2122\t2295\t173\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"When people fall in love with someone,\r\r\n"
"they naturally want to know every last detail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2311\t2439\t128\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Their blood type, birthplace,\r\r\n"
"fashion preferences, family..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2463\t2557\t94\t　\t　\t "
msgid "The more they learn, the more connected they feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2580\t2725\t145\t　\t　\t "
msgid "On the contrary, if that person seems unattainable..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2733\t2833\t100\t　\t　\t "
msgid "It only further fuels the thirst for knowledge."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2864\t3056\t192\tOK\t　\t "
msgid ""
"They want to know everything. Bring even\r\r\n"
"the slightest little secrets out into the sun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3084\t3144\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "You mean Haruka's past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3168\t3286\t118\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Yes. Love can be a cruel thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3319\t3495\t176\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Once someone feels betrayed by the object\r\r\n"
"of their affection, love can soon turn to hatred."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3525\t3585\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Wouldn't you agree?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3809\t3869\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "It's for her own good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3894\t4040\t146\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"If we erase your connection to Haruka,\r\n"
"I'll be able to protect her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4046\t4106\t60\t分\t　\t "
msgid "In short..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4117\t4199\t82\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Got it. I've heard enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4225\t4281\t56\t　\t　\t60ｆ以下です"
msgid "And your answer?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4282\t4371\t89\t　\t　\t "
msgid "I'm not leaving. Not a chance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4463\t4634\t171\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"My kids still need me. They'd be\r\r\n"
"heartbroken if I walked out on them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4675\t4815\t140\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"As long as they're living here,\r\r\n"
"I'm not going anywhere."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4939\t5006\t67\t　\t　\t "
msgid "So this is a matter of duty."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5031\t5104\t73\t　\t　\t "
msgid "It's a lot deeper than that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5146\t5232\t86\t　\t　\t "
msgid "This is the path I've chosen in life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5315\t5426\t111\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Now if you'll excuse me, I have things to do.\r\n"
"You can see yourself out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5486\t5552\t66\t　\t　\t "
msgid "I must say, I'm surprised."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5679\t5850\t171\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"For someone who's led the life you have,\r\r\n"
"you know nothing about how the world works."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6085\t6274\t189\tOk\t　\t "
msgid ""
"You can't even make one little girl's\r\r\n"
"wishes come true. You realize that, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6442\t6584\t142\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"And it's not just her. I noticed something\r\r\n"
"during my visit the other day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6658\t6718\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "This is where dreams come to die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6761\t6845\t84\t分\t　\t "
msgid "As long as you're here, that is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6898\t6958\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "What's that supposed to mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7037\t7194\t157\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"I asked your children if they were happy...\r\r\n"
"And they all gave me the same response."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7201\t7261\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "It was yes, of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7291\t7436\t145\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"For a child with no family, this place\r\r\n"
"must feel like heaven on earth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7474\t7601\t127\t　\t　\t "
msgid "But the truth is, they're all afraid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7698\t7758\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Afraid of what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7808\t7903\t95\t　\t　\t "
msgid "That one day this fragile happiness will shatter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8196\t8315\t119\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Your children clearly love you,\r\r\n"
"from the bottom of their hearts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8336\t8471\t135\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"At the same time, they also love\r\r\n"
"the happy, peaceful life you provide for them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8472\t8581\t109\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"So much that they'd sacrifice\r\r\n"
"anything just to hang on to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8598\t8680\t82\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Even their own aspirations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8870\t9012\t142\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Kids should be free to be a little\r\r\n"
"selfish. Free to chase their dreams."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9014\t9074\t60\t分\t　\t "
msgid "Free to be true to themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9120\t9278\t158\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"As long as you're here, your children\r\r\n"
"will never have that freedom."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9349\t9409\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9461\t9521\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "You know it deep down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9535\t9711\t176\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"If your children are ever going to grow up,\r\r\n"
"they need an ambition to strive for."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9752\t9935\t183\tOK\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Say one person clings to the safety of their current\r\r\n"
"circumstance, while another doggedly pursues their goal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9959\t10031\t72\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Who will be stronger in the end?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10147\t10271\t124\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Let Haruka-chan embark on this journey.\r\r\n"
"You have one of your own to make."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10292\t10389\t97\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Not for others, but for yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10399\t10459\t60\t分\t　\t "
msgid "Pursue your own goal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10480\t10523\t43\t　\t　\t60ｆ以下です"
msgid "But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10524\t10717\t193\tOK\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Leave your daughter to me. In return, I'll fund\r\r\n"
"the future of every child who calls this place home."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10742\t10894\t152\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"I'll cover their living expenses.\r\r\n"
"Make sure they can grow and thrive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10900\t10975\t75\t　\t　\t "
msgid "They won't have a want in the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11027\t11120\t93\t　\t　\t "
msgid "I'll even let you choose your own replacement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11262\t11385\t123\t　\t　\t "
msgid "And I promise you. Haruka-chan will be a star."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11410\t11550\t140\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Just grant her this wish.\r\r\n"
"Let her be the singer she wants to be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11600\t11685\t85\t　\t　\t "
msgid "My... wish?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11748\t11808\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "What makes you so sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11840\t11994\t154\t　\t　\t "
msgid ""
"How could you possibly know what Haruka\r\r\n"
"really wants? Why you, of all people?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12026\t12086\t60\t　\t　\t "
msgid "It's simple."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12115\t12177\t62\t　\t　\t "
msgid "Because I wanted the same thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12219\t12300\t81\t　\t　\t "
msgid "You had... the same dream?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12302\t12426\t124\t\t　\t "
msgid "Yes. As long as you find the right successor..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12438\t12530\t79\t\t　\t "
msgid ""
"Someone else can pick up the torch.\r\r\n"
"Carry out your dream."
msgstr ""